# {{ project_name }}

A RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation) application built with ragbits.
You can read more about ragbits [here](https://ragbits.deepsense.ai).

## Getting Started

1. Install dependencies:
```bash
uv sync
```

2. Run docker compose:
```bash
docker compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml up -d
```

3. Run the ingestion script:
```bash
uv run ragbits document-search ingest web://https://arxiv.org/pdf/2310.06825
```

3. Run the main script:
```bash
uv run ragbits api run {{pkg_name}}.app:ChatApp
```
